des:
Smart Life - Smart Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to control your devices！
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your Smart Life - Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Smart Life - Smart Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Smart Life - Smart Home account in our "Smart Life - Smart Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Smart Life - Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Smart Life - Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Smart Life - Smart Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smart Life - Smart Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smart Life - Smart Home", and you'll be navigated to Smart Life - Smart Home login page;
(9). Input your Smart Life - Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off the air conditioner.
Alexa, set the bedroom fan speed to auto
Alexa, what is the bedroom fan speed?
Alexa, decrease the fan speed on the bedroom fan.
